<L>__{interior opera house night 1780's}
<A>__{we see the tableau on stage with the count kneeling to the countess. all are singing.}
<C>__{old salieri }
<D>__{i saw a woman disguised in her maid's clothes hear her husband speak the first tender words he has offered her in years, only because he thinks she is someone else. i heard the music of true forgiveness filling the theatre, conferring on all who sat there a perfect absolution. god was singing through this little man to all the world unstoppable making my defeat more bitter with each passing bar.}
